Peter Borrmann wrote:

> Hi,
> does anybody know how to measure the time between two
> trigger signals as precise as possible ( around 10 microseconds
> would be fine.)  with the handyboard.
>
> Peter

Use the TIC port 2 or 3.

The precision of the reading you'll get is 0.5 us.

About a year ago I posted some drivers to make such measurements.
Tell me if you want them.

